snippet.title: Caterpillar Construction Zone Full Playthrough (Game Boy Color)
snippet.description: This is one of my all time favorite Game Boy Color Games Caterpillar Construction Zone I'll be doing a Full Playthrough in 1 Hour in one video. So anyway I hope you enjoy the video!, Information About This game: Released in December 1999, Rated E for Everyone, Publisher Mattel Interactive, Developer Realtime Associates, For the Nintendo Game Boy Color.
